msgstr "一種大型爆破彈，尺寸約為.50勃朗寧機槍彈的兩倍，重量更是數倍。"

#: .\at_ammo.json
msgid "33x308mm IHEAT"
msgid_plural "33x308mm IHEATs"
msgstr[0] "33x308毫米IHEAT彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '33x308mm IHEAT'}
#: .\at_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A large shell with a label near the bottom of the casing; WARNING DO NOT "
"FIRE WITHIN 80FT OF FREINDLY UNITS. this is probably very explosive."
msgstr "一種大型炮彈，彈殼底部附近有標籤：警告，不要在80英尺內對友軍單位開火。這可能極具爆炸性。"

