#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "advanced power armor"
msgid_plural "advanced power armors"
msgstr[0] "先進動力裝甲"

#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'advanced power armor'}.
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "You sheath your %s"
msgstr "你將你的%s收鞘。"

#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'advanced power armor'}.
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "Sheath knife"
msgstr "收鞘刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'advanced power armor'}
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid ""
"A jet black suit of very lightweight powered armor, designed to be used by "
"specialist shock troopers. Known only by the military designation 'Power "
"Armor, Advanced', it appears to have been constructed in limited quantities."
msgstr "一套烏黑、非常輕便的動力裝甲，專為特種突擊部隊設計。僅以軍用代號“先進動力裝甲”為人所知，似乎產量有限。"

#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "advanced power armor helmet"
msgid_plural "advanced power armor helmets"
msgstr[0] "先進動力裝甲頭盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'advanced power armor helmet'}
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid ""
"A jet black power armor helmet designed for use with the matching suit, "
"constructed from lightweight materials, but still very protective."
msgstr "一頂烏黑的動力裝甲頭盔，專為配套裝甲設計，採用輕質材料製成，但仍提供極佳防護。"

#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "robot helmet"
msgid_plural "robot helmets"
msgstr[0] "機器人頭盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'robot helmet'}
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid ""
"A tough green helmet built from durable materials, designed as armor for "
"combat robots, but suitable for humans."
msgstr "一頂堅固的綠色頭盔，由耐用材料製成，原為戰鬥機器人設計的護甲，但也適合人類使用。"

#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "steel helmet"
msgid_plural "steel helmets"
msgstr[0] "鋼盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'steel helmet'}
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid ""
"A dull gray steel helmet with a skirt on the rear to protect against "
"shrapnel and provide extra coverage."
msgstr "一頂暗灰色鋼盔，後部帶有護裙，用於防禦彈片並提供額外覆蓋。"

#: .\at_armor.json
msgid "pilot helmet"
msgid_plural "pilot helmets"
msgstr[0] "飛行員頭盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pilot helmet'}
#: .\at_armor.json
msgid ""
"A thick helmet, encasing the entire head, with a large reflective visor, "
"allowing a wide field of vision."
msgstr "一頂厚重的頭盔，完全包裹頭部，配有大型反光面罩，提供寬闊視野。"

#: .\at_armor.json
