#: .\at_books.json
msgid "Man or Machine"
msgid_plural "Man or Machines"
msgstr[0] "人還是機器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Man or Machine'}
#: .\at_books.json
msgid ""
"The first book of the \"Man or Machine\" series, focused on the electronics "
"component of robots and cyborgs. While very complex and certainly not an "
"entry-level text, it does offer many pointers and tips to even the veteran "
"programmer. Contains a few diagrams and ideas for programs that you could "
"apply to your own garage-level projects."
msgstr ""
"“人還是機器”系列的第一本書，專注於機器人與半機械人的電子元件。內容非常複雜，絕非入門讀物，但即使對資深程序員也提供了許多提示與技巧。包含一些圖表和程序構想，可應用於你自己的車庫級項目。"

#: .\at_books.json
msgid "Man or Machine: Book Two"
msgid_plural "Man or Machine: Book Twos"
msgstr[0] "人還是機器：第二冊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Man or Machine: Book Two'}
#: .\at_books.json
msgid ""
"The second entry in an extensively detailed series documenting the "
"construction of advanced robots and cyborgs. This book is centered on the "
"more \"hands on\" aspect of biomechanics and robots. It features many "
"different recipes, that with some enginuity, could possibly be used even in "
"a post-cataclysm enviroment."
msgstr ""
"這是一本詳盡記錄高級機器人與生化人建造過程的系列叢書中的第二冊。本書側重於生物力學與機器人領域中更為“實踐操作”的方面。書中包含多種不同的配方，憑藉一定的巧思，甚至可在災後環境中加以運用。"

#: .\at_books.json
msgid "Man or Machine, Book Three"
msgid_plural "Man or Machine, Book Threes"
msgstr[0] "《人與機器，第三冊》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Man or Machine, Book Three'}
#: .\at_books.json
msgid ""
"The third book in a three book series on robotics and cyborgs. This book "
"covers the biomechanic aspects, with some rather gruesome photos and "
"detailed descriptions, however, it has a wealth of knowledge, and even some "
"rudimentary designs. With some adaptations, most of the documents within "
"could be applied to your own works."
msgstr ""
"這是關於機器人學與生化人的三卷系列叢書中的第三冊。本書涵蓋了生物力學方面的內容，附有一些相當駭人的照片和詳細描述，然而其中蘊含豐富的知識，甚至包括一些基礎設計。經過適當調整，書內大部分文檔均可應用於您自己的作品中。"

#: .\at_books.json
msgid "Heavy Mech Machinery"
msgid_plural "Heavy Mech Machinerys"
msgstr[0] "重型機甲機械"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Heavy Mech Machinery'}
#: .\at_books.json
msgid ""
"A thick binder detailing the operation, maintenance and construction of "
"mechs, with much insight into the internal mechanisms."
msgstr "一本厚重的活頁夾，詳細闡述了機甲的操作、維護與建造，並對內部機制提供了深入見解。"

#: .\at_combustion.json
msgid "A combustion engine.  Burns fuel from a tank in the vehicle."
msgstr "一臺內燃機。燃燒車輛油箱中的燃料。"

#: .\at_combustion.json
msgid ""
"A combustion engine.  Burns diesel fuel from a tank in the vehicle.  Can "
"also burn biodiesel or lamp oil, though somewhat less efficiently."
msgstr "一臺內燃機。燃燒車輛油箱中的柴油燃料。也可燃燒生物柴油或燈油，但效率稍低。"

#: .\at_combustion.json
msgid ""
"An advanced combustion engine.  Burns gasoline or diesel or aviation fuel "
"from a tank in the vehicle.  Can also burn lamp oil, though somewhat less "
"efficiently.  Better power-to-weight ratio than a traditional engine, but "
"consumes more fuel."
msgstr "一臺先進的內燃機。燃燒車輛油箱中的汽油、柴油或航空燃料。也可燃燒燈油，但效率稍低。相比傳統發動機具有更好的功率重量比，但消耗更多燃料。"

