"a huge ammo box mounted on your back similar to a backpack with thousands of"
" rounds of ammunition, the ammo feeds to the respective weapon via a link "
"with rounds on a belt,when fired you can see the rounds zipping through the "
"chain-feed."
msgstr "一個巨大的彈藥箱，類似揹包般背在背上，裝有數千發彈藥。彈藥通過彈鏈連接輸送至相應武器，開火時你能看到子彈在鏈式供彈系統中飛速穿行。"

#: .\at_magazines.json
