#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Roboticist"
msgstr "機器人專家"

#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Roboticist"
msgstr "機器人專家"

#. ~ Profession (male Roboticist) description
#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Fascinated with robots and machines since you were a child, you started a "
"small workshop, building robots for government contracts and neighborhood "
"children alike."
msgstr "自幼痴迷於機器人與機械，你開設了一家小型工作室，為政府合同和鄰里孩童製造機器人。"

#. ~ Profession (female Roboticist) description
#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Fascinated with robots and machines since you were a child, you started a "
"small workshop, building robots for government contracts and neighborhood "
"children alike."
msgstr "自幼痴迷於機器人與機械，你開設了一家小型工作室，為政府合同和鄰里孩童製造機器人。"

#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Biomechanist"
msgstr "生物機械師"

#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Biomechanist"
msgstr "生物機械師"

#. ~ Profession (male Biomechanist) description
#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You've always wondered what made things work, and people were no different. "
"Once you had figured out what made it tick, you wanted to improve them, and "
"what is better than sophisticated upgrades for people like strapping on a "
"fusion blaster, or implanting a cerebral booster?"
msgstr ""
"你一直好奇事物運作的原理，人類也不例外。一旦弄清了機制，你就想改進他們，還有什麼比給人裝上精密的升級更好呢？比如加裝聚變衝擊炮，或植入大腦增強器。"

#. ~ Profession (female Biomechanist) description
#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You've always wondered what made things work, and people were no different. "
"Once you had figured out what made it tick, you wanted to improve them, and "
"what is better than sophisticated upgrades for people like strapping on a "
"fusion blaster, or implanting a cerebral booster?"
msgstr ""
"你一直好奇事物運作的原理，人類也不例外。一旦弄清了機制，你就想改進他們，還有什麼比給人裝上精密的升級更好呢？比如加裝聚變衝擊炮，或植入大腦增強器。"

#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Mech Pilot"
msgstr "機甲駕駛員"

#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Mech Pilot"
msgstr "機甲駕駛員"

#. ~ Profession (male Mech Pilot) description
#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You were trained as an elite pilot, to operate the newly prototyped combat "
"mech suits, the government's response to captured Chinese intel."
msgstr "你受過精英飛行員訓練，操作新原型戰鬥機甲套裝，這是政府對獲取的中國情報的回應。"

#. ~ Profession (female Mech Pilot) description
#: .\at_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You were trained as an elite pilot, to operate the newly prototyped combat "
"mech suits, the government's response to captured Chinese intel."
msgstr "你受過精英飛行員訓練，操作新原型戰鬥機甲套裝，這是政府對獲取的中國情報的回應。"

#: .\at_rams.json
msgid ""
"A reinforced ram.  Place at the edge of vehicle to reduce damage taken in "
"collisions, and to increase damaged delivered in collisions, if the ram is "
"the first vehicle part to collide."
msgstr "加固衝撞杆。安裝在車輛邊緣，減少碰撞時受到的傷害，並在衝撞杆作為首個碰撞部件時增加造成的傷害。"

#: .\at_rams.json
msgid "military bullbar"
msgstr "軍用防撞杆"

#: .\at_rams.json
msgid "military rambar"
msgstr "軍用防撞杆"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M35-H railgun"
msgid_plural "M35-H railguns"
msgstr[0] "M35-H 軌道炮"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A military developed railgun prototype, designed for mounted applications. "
"Built in decent numbers for extensive field testing. Although it was never "
"offically deployed before the cataclysm struck, it was in the process of "
"being approved. Due to high recoil, and unwieldly size, this weapon is only "
"possible to use deployed or in mounted applications."
msgstr ""
"一款軍方開發的軌道炮原型，專為車載或固定式應用設計。為進行廣泛的實地測試而生產了相當數量。儘管在大災變爆發前從未正式部署，但已處於審批階段。由於後坐力巨大且體積笨重，此武器僅能在部署或固定式應用中使用。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "USAS 20"
msgid_plural "USAS 20s"
msgstr[0] "USAS 20"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"The USAS 20 looks like a boxy upsized caricature of the M16A2.  Like its "
"Auto Assault-12 predecessor, it is a select-fire shotgun fed from large box "
"or drum magazines.  The in-line recoil system and sheer weight make for "
"pleasant shooting."
msgstr ""
"USAS 20 看起來像是 M16A2 的放大版方塊狀誇張造型。與其前身 Auto Assault-12 "
"類似，它是一款可選擇射擊模式的霰彈槍，使用大型彈匣或彈鼓供彈。其直列式後坐系統和巨大重量使得射擊體驗相當舒適。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "Desert Eagle .660"
msgid_plural "Desert Eagle .660"
msgstr[0] "沙漠之鷹 .660"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"One of the most recognizable handguns due to its popularity in movies and "
"video games, the Desert Eagle is better known for its menacing appearance "
"than its performance.  It's a large pistol, but its heavy weight reduces "
"recoil. This one has been manufactured and upsized to use .660 supermag."
msgstr ""
"作為電影和電子遊戲中的常客，沙漠之鷹是最具辨識度的手槍之一，其威猛外觀比實際性能更為出名。這是一款大型手槍，但沉重的重量有助於減少後坐力。此型號經過製造和放大，可使用"
" .660 超級馬格南彈藥。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M9887"
msgid_plural "M9887s"
msgstr[0] "M9887"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "What looks to be a AR-15 scaled up and bored out to use 11mm rounds."
msgstr "看起來像是 AR-15 的放大版，並擴膛以使用 11 毫米彈藥。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "semi-auto"
msgstr "半自動"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "burst"
msgstr "連發"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自動"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "AK50"
msgid_plural "AK50s"
msgstr[0] "AK50"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"One of the most recognizable assault rifles ever made, converted by some "
"youtuber to use .50 BMG."
msgstr "史上最具辨識度的突擊步槍之一，被某位 YouTube 博主改裝以使用 .50 BMG 彈藥。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "K.O.R.D HMG"
msgid_plural "K.O.R.D HMG"
msgstr[0] "K.O.R.D 重機槍"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A heavy machine gun used by the Russian military. Tends to be mounted on "
"vehicles due to its massive recoil and size. However it has a fairly low "
"weight, and given a strong enough person it could be wielded effectively "
"(unlike the M2 Browning.)"
msgstr ""
"俄羅斯軍隊使用的一款重機槍。由於其巨大的後坐力和尺寸，通常安裝在車輛上。然而，它的重量相對較輕，若使用者足夠強壯，也能有效手持使用（與 M2 "
"勃朗寧不同）。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "S M85-V1.1"
msgid_plural "S M85-V1.1"
msgstr[0] "S M85-V1.1"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A hulking mass of a revolver even dwarfing the Model 500. Extremely heavy."
msgstr "一款龐大的轉輪手槍，甚至比 Model 500 還要巨大。極其沉重。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M220022a2 SPLASH"
msgid_plural "M220022a2 SPLASH"
msgstr[0] "M220022a2 濺射"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A shoulder mounted ATGM system designed to replace the old disposable rocket"
" launchers, intended for use with power armor.  It has four barrels for ATGM"
" rockets."
msgstr "一款肩扛式反坦克導彈系統，旨在取代舊式一次性火箭筒，設計用於動力裝甲。它配備四個反坦克導彈發射管。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "single shot"
msgstr "單發"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "all barrels"
msgstr "全管齊射"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M14070a1 Bolt"
msgid_plural "M14070a1 Bolts"
msgstr[0] "M14070a1 螺栓"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A military developed anti-power armor weapon mounted on the shoulder, "
"similarly to a rocket launcher. Designed for use by power armour against "
"power armour, only a few exist numbering in the hundreds. Never deployed, "
"and in perfect condition."
msgstr "一款軍方開發的反動力裝甲武器，類似於火箭筒，安裝在肩部。設計用於動力裝甲對抗動力裝甲，僅存數百件，數量稀少。從未部署，且狀態完美。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "duo"
msgstr "雙發"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "high-auto"
msgstr "高速自動"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M14083 Storm"
msgid_plural "M14083 Storms"
msgstr[0] "M14083 風暴"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A military developed anti-power armor autocannon wielded only by soldiers "
"with power armor, made for shredding vehicles and people alike. Only a few "
"exist numbering in the low hundreds. Never deployed, and in perfect "
"condition."
msgstr "一款軍方開發的反動力裝甲自動炮，僅由穿戴動力裝甲的士兵使用，用於撕裂車輛和人員。僅存數百件，數量稀少。從未部署，且狀態完美。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "trio"
msgstr "三連發"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "full auto"
msgstr "全自動"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "rifle"
msgstr "步槍"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M14024a4 Hail"
msgid_plural "M14024a4 Hails"
msgstr[0] "M14024a4 冰雹"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A military developed anti-infantry superheavy machine gun wielded by only "
"those with power armor, made for shredding enemy infantry en masse."
msgstr "一款軍方開發的反步兵超重型機槍，僅由穿戴動力裝甲者使用，用於大規模撕裂敵方步兵。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "semi"
msgstr "半自動"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "low-auto"
msgstr "低自動"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M14026a1 Rend"
msgid_plural "M14026a1 Rends"
msgstr[0] "M14026a1 撕裂者"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"The apex of anti-infantry weapons, no ground weapon can compare to its anti-"
"infantry shredding power."
msgstr "反步兵武器的巔峰，沒有任何地面武器能與之匹敵其撕裂步兵的威力。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "over-auto"
msgstr "超自動"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M14092"
msgid_plural "M14092s"
msgstr[0] "M14092"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A bigass shoulder mounted cannon for mobile bunker busting. But seriously, "
"this thing is huge."
msgstr "一門巨大的肩扛式火炮，用於機動摧毀碉堡。但說真的，這東西太大了。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M34-L railgun"
msgid_plural "M34-L railguns"
msgstr[0] "M34-L 軌道炮"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A military developed railgun prototype, designed for use by infantry. Has a "
"rotating cylinder, holding twelve H&K 12mm ferromagnetic slugs."
msgstr "一款軍方開發的軌道炮原型，設計供步兵使用。配備旋轉彈巢，可容納十二發H&K 12毫米鐵磁彈丸。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "M26-b Gatling"
msgid_plural "M26-b Gatlings"
msgstr[0] "M26-b 加特林"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid ""
"A large cannon consisting of a large motor, belt feed system, and firing "
"mechanism, employing eight long barrels mounted on a rotating disc. The use "
"of eight barrels allows for high rates of fire and increased heat "
"dissipation. Firing this weapon is impossible without a mount, due to the "
"sheer size and weight."
msgstr ""
"一門大型火炮，由大型電機、彈鏈供彈系統和擊發機構組成，採用八根長槍管安裝在旋轉盤上。八根槍管的使用允許高射速和增強散熱。由於尺寸和重量巨大，沒有支架無法發射此武器。"

#: .\at_ranged.json
msgid "semi auto"
msgstr "半自動"

#: .\at_snippets.json
msgid ""
"This is an advertisement for Wily Industries's Geologically Unstable Terrain"
" Surveyor.  It shows large robot wearing a construction hardhat preventing a"
" fallen boulder from crushing a worker."
msgstr "這是威利工業公司地質不穩定地形勘測器的廣告。展示了一個戴著建築安全帽的大型機器人，防止落石壓垮工人。"

#: .\at_snippets.json
msgid ""
"This is one of the many posters printed by Wily Industries, before the "
"cataclysm. This poster features a sniper robot's green helmet, with the "
"trademark eerily glowing eye. The caption reads, in bold  \"KEEP QUIET, "
"CARELESS TALK COSTS LIVES.\""
msgstr ""
"這是威利工業公司在災變前印製的眾多海報之一。這張海報以狙擊機器人的綠色頭盔為特色，帶有標誌性的詭異發光眼睛。標題用粗體寫著：“保持安靜，閒談危及生命。”"

#: .\at_snippets.json
msgid ""
"This is a poster printed by Wily Industries. This poster depicts a Met Civil"
" Protector robot, in black, red and white. The caption reads, in bold  \"WE "
"WILL KEEP YOU SAFE.\""
msgstr "這是威利工業公司印製的一張海報。這張海報描繪了一個Met民用保護者機器人，採用黑、紅、白三色。標題用粗體寫著：“我們將保障您的安全。”"

#: .\at_snippets.json
msgid ""
"This is a poster printed by Wily Industries. This poster depicts a Met Civil"
" Protector robot, in black, red and white. The caption reads, in bold  \"DO "
"NOT COMPROMISE YOUR SAFETY.\""
msgstr "這是威利工業公司印製的一張海報。這張海報描繪了一個Met民用保護者機器人，採用黑、紅、白三色。標題用粗體寫著：“切勿妥協您的安全。”"

#: .\at_snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Those creepy-ass mets aren't as tough as the helmet robots, but they don't"
" seem to do much anyways.\""
msgstr "“那些該死的Met機器人沒有頭盔機器人那麼硬，但它們似乎也沒啥大用。”"

#: .\at_snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"I met this cyborg, pretty friendly, unlike the majority. I chatted with "
"him about various things, pretty decent, but man, what kind of messed up "
"stories he was telling me. That he saw some shit they were doing in these "
"labs long before all this mess. Creatures, not even humans, compared to him,"
" made out of blob. Yeah, artificial blob humans that just like him were "
"turned into cyborgs. What kind of shit is this? Did they know about all this"
" long before it happened? Man, it's messed up. I don't know.\""
msgstr ""
"“我遇到了一個賽博格，挺友好的，不像大多數。我和他聊了各種事情，人還不錯，但天哪，他給我講的那些破事。他說早在這一切混亂之前，就看到他們在這些實驗室裡搞的一些勾當。那些生物，甚至不是人類，和他相比，是用粘液造出來的。是啊，人工粘液人類，就像他一樣被改造成了賽博格。這算什麼事？他們是不是早就知道這一切會發生？夥計，這太亂了。我不知道。”"

#: .\at_species.json
msgid "cyborg"
msgid_plural "cyborgs"
msgstr[0] "賽博格"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"I never asked for this!\""
msgstr "“我從未要求過這個！”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"What am I?\""
msgstr "“我是什麼？”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"Am I a human?\""
msgstr "“我是人類嗎？”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"I will serve! Oh, God!\""
msgstr "“我將效勞！哦，天哪！”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"I was made to serve!\""
msgstr "“我被製造出來就是為了效勞！”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"All of my systems are online.\""
msgstr "“我所有系統都在線。”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"I'm... alive as a human?\""
msgstr "“我……像人類一樣活著？”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"Ready for combat!\""
msgstr "“準備戰鬥！”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"All systems operational.\""
msgstr "“所有系統運作正常。”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"Selective cognitive suppressant unit running at maximal efficiency.\""
msgstr "“選擇性認知抑制單元以最高效率運行。”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"Combat systems nominal.\""
msgstr "“戰鬥系統正常。”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"Security program functional.\""
msgstr "“安全程序功能正常。”"

#: .\at_speech.json
msgid "\"Unit transmitter online.\""
msgstr "\"單位發射器已上線。\""

#: .\at_tools.json
msgid "robotics toolkit"
msgid_plural "robotics toolkits"
msgstr[0] "機器人工具包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'robotics toolkit'}
#: .\at_tools.json
msgid ""
"This is a cutting-edge piece of technology: a portable, laser precision, "
"computer assisted, miniature robotics work shop. Designed to construct small"
" electronics and similar devices, it features an easy to use GUI and is "
"capable of creating sophisticated electronics and high grade robotics. May "
"also be suitable for gunsmithing."
msgstr ""
"這是一件尖端科技產品：一個便攜式、激光精密、計算機輔助的微型機器人工作坊。專為製造小型電子設備及類似裝置而設計，它配備了易於使用的圖形用戶界面，能夠製造精密的電子元件和高品質的機器人。或許也適用於槍械製造。"

#: .\at_tools.json
msgid "monomolecular machete"
msgid_plural "monomolecular machetes"
msgstr[0] "單分子砍刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular machete'}
#: .\at_tools.json
msgid ""
"A foot-long blade made from high-tech alloy and edged with bonded "
"nanocrystals, removed from a cyborg, and converted into a machete."
