"Adds advanced craftable vehicle parts, mech parts to craft vehicle mechs, "
"craftable blob cyborgs, some new robots, some new armors, weapons and "
"crafting."
msgstr "添加可製作的先進車輛部件、用於製造車輛機甲的機甲部件、可製作的粘液生化人、一些新機器人、新裝甲、武器和製作內容。"

#: .\vehicles_at.json
msgid "M1070 Oshkosh placeholder"
msgstr "M1070奧什科什佔位符"

#: .\cyborg\at_activateable_cyborgs.json
msgid "hibernating blob cyborg"
msgid_plural "hibernating blob cyborgs"
msgstr[0] "休眠中的粘液生化人"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'hibernating blob cyborg'}.
#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'hibernating heavy blob cyborg'}.
#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'hibernating advanced blob cyborg'}.
#: .\cyborg\at_activateable_cyborgs.json
msgid "The blob cyborg activates, and raises to it's feet."
msgstr "粘液生化人激活，並站立起來。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'hibernating blob cyborg'}.
#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'hibernating heavy blob cyborg'}.
#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'hibernating advanced blob cyborg'}.
#: .\cyborg\at_activateable_cyborgs.json
msgid "You've activated the blob cyborg improperly, and it attacks!"
msgstr "你錯誤地激活了粘液生化人，它發起了攻擊！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hibernating blob cyborg'}
#: .\cyborg\at_activateable_cyborgs.json
msgid ""
"This is an inactive blob cyborg, composed of an artificial blob human, "
"several bionic upgrades, and some limiters and control systems."
msgstr "這是一個非活躍的粘液生化人，由人工粘液人類、若干仿生升級部件以及一些限制器和控制系統組成。"

#: .\cyborg\at_activateable_cyborgs.json
msgid "hibernating heavy blob cyborg"
msgid_plural "hibernating heavy blob cyborgs"
msgstr[0] "休眠中的重型粘液生化人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hibernating heavy blob cyborg'}
#: .\cyborg\at_activateable_cyborgs.json
msgid ""
"This is an inactive blob cyborg, sturdy in it's construction, with many "
"pieces of extra hardware attached, and a thick steel skin, covering it's "
"advanced electronics and life sustaining systems. It it's current state, "
"this cyborg is probably less blob man than machine."
msgstr ""
"這是一個非活躍的粘液生化人，結構堅固，附有許多額外硬件，並覆蓋著厚實的鋼皮，保護其先進的電子設備和生命維持系統。在目前狀態下，這個生化人可能更像機器而非粘液人。"

#: .\cyborg\at_activateable_cyborgs.json
msgid "hibernating advanced blob cyborg"
msgid_plural "hibernating advanced blob cyborgs"
msgstr[0] "休眠中的高級粘液生化人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hibernating advanced blob cyborg'}
#: .\cyborg\at_activateable_cyborgs.json
msgid ""
"A sturdy mechanical body, with little in the way of artificial organic "
"matter visible. It has what appears to be segments of power armor grafted to"
" its skin and steel frame, with cybernetic augmentations protruding."
msgstr "一個堅固的機械軀體，幾乎看不到人工有機物質。其表面和鋼架上似乎移植了動力裝甲的片段，並有賽博格增強部件突出。"

#: .\cyborg\at_cyborg_components.json
msgid "advanced organic-interfacing processor unit"
msgid_plural "advanced organic-interfacing processor units"
msgstr[0] "高級有機接口處理器單元"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'advanced organic-interfacing processor unit'}
#: .\cyborg\at_cyborg_components.json
msgid ""
"A large mass of wiring, chips, and circuits encased in plastic, all running "
"in parallel to operate a cyborg's motor skills and life support systems. Can"
" attach to an artificial blob version of a human brain to add additional "
"functionalities."
msgstr "一大團電線、芯片和電路封裝在塑料中，並行運行以控制生化人的運動技能和生命維持系統。可連接到人工粘液版本的人類大腦以增加額外功能。"

#: .\cyborg\at_cyborg_components.json
msgid "augmented heart"
msgid_plural "augmented hearts"
msgstr[0] "增強心臟"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'augmented heart'}
#: .\cyborg\at_cyborg_components.json
msgid ""
"An artificial blob heart encapsulated in a protective plastic case, guarding"
" against both decay and damage. Many wires and sensors protrude from the "
"artificial blob flesh, with several cables and hoses extending from the "
"exterior of the case."
msgstr "一個人工粘液心臟封裝在保護性塑料殼中，防止腐爛和損壞。許多電線和傳感器從人工粘液組織中伸出，殼體外側延伸出數條電纜和軟管。"

#: .\cyborg\at_cyborg_components.json
msgid "synthetic eye"
msgid_plural "synthetic eyes"
msgstr[0] "合成眼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'synthetic eye'}
#: .\cyborg\at_cyborg_components.json
msgid ""
"A spherical steel object, comprised of high quality lenses, a camera, and "
"circuitry designed to be able to send readable data to either a human brain,"
" artificial blob version of a human brain or an electronic system."
msgstr "一個球形鋼製物體，由高質量透鏡、攝像頭和電路組成，設計用於向人類大腦、人工粘液版本的人類大腦或電子系統發送可讀數據。"

#: .\cyborg\at_cyborg_components.json
msgid "cybernetic lung"
msgid_plural "cybernetic lungs"
msgstr[0] "賽博格肺"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cybernetic lung'}
#: .\cyborg\at_cyborg_components.json
msgid ""
"A chunk of plastic barely resembling a lung. Only the outer piece is totally"
" inorganic, with a silver-platinum alloy used as a antimicrobal and air "
"filtration agent inside the artificial organic interior."
msgstr "一塊勉強像肺的塑料塊。只有外層完全是無機物，人工有機內部使用了銀鉑合金作為抗菌和空氣過濾劑。"

#: .\cyborg\at_cyborg_components.json
msgid "artificial blood purifier"
msgid_plural "artificial blood purifiers"
msgstr[0] "人工血液淨化器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'artificial blood purifier'}
#: .\cyborg\at_cyborg_components.json
msgid ""
"A completely artificial organ designed to keep a cyborg's blood clean and "
"free from parasites and infections. Functionally similar to a human kidney."
msgstr "一個完全人造的器官，旨在保持生化人的血液清潔，免受寄生蟲和感染。功能上類似於人類腎臟。"

#: .\cyborg\at_cyborg_components.json
msgid "cyborg frame"
msgid_plural "cyborg frames"
msgstr[0] "生化人框架"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cyborg frame'}
#: .\cyborg\at_cyborg_components.json
msgid ""
"An artificial blob human body that has been thoroughly dissected, and is now"
" covered with incisions of various sizes, allowing the many modifications to"
" the skeletal structure."
msgstr "一個被徹底解剖的人工人體團塊，現在覆蓋著各種大小的切口，允許對骨骼結構進行大量改造。"

#: .\cyborg\at_cyborg_components.json
msgid "heavy cyborg frame"
msgid_plural "heavy cyborg frames"
msgstr[0] "重型生化人框架"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'heavy cyborg frame'}
#: .\cyborg\at_cyborg_components.json
msgid ""
"An artificial blob human body that has been dissected and augmented to a "
"high degree. Little of the original skeleton is present, having been mostly "
"replaced with hardened steel, and has sections of armor plating grafted to "
"it's skin."
msgstr "一個被解剖並高度增強的人工人體團塊。原始骨架所剩無幾，大部分已被硬化鋼取代，並有裝甲板部分移植到其皮膚上。"

#: .\robot\at_activateable_robots.json
msgid "inactive sniper joe"
msgid_plural "inactive sniper joes"
msgstr[0] "休眠的狙擊喬"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive sniper joe'}.
#: .\robot\at_activateable_robots.json
msgid "The sniper joe activates and it's visor glows eerily."
msgstr "狙擊喬激活了，它的面罩發出詭異的微光。"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive sniper joe'}.
#: .\robot\at_activateable_robots.json
msgid "You've made a mistake, and the sniper joe turns on you!"
msgstr "你犯了個錯誤，狙擊喬轉而攻擊你！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive sniper joe'}
#: .\robot\at_activateable_robots.json
msgid ""
